page.title: 01Introduction
page.content: For our{Domesday Survey}we have attempted to present a picture of Chandag Junior School in 1985. It has taken us a month of hard work to collect this information.We have tried to make our description of what it is like to live in Keynsham as detailed as possible.We have completed hedge,land use and house surveys as well as describing two local events i.e.the hospital fete and the school fair.We have also included a description of a walk to Chewton Keynsham,three accounts of what it is like to live in Keynsham in 1985 and some information about Keynsham Cricket Club.
